Man:
Oh, shit.

07:49.917 --> 07:51.458
Anderson:
Based on what
you've done so far,

07:51.542 --> 07:54.083
this area will be covered
with your reflective sand.

07:54.166 --> 07:56.500
Roughly, how much longer
will the ice last?

