The prediction is days.

07:58.542 --> 08:01.000
Uh, and-- and that
matters on this scale.

08:01.083 --> 08:04.125
Smith:
The long-term goal is
to scale up the process

08:04.208 --> 08:06.083
and pinpoint the areas
in the Arctic

08:06.166 --> 08:08.125
where it will have
the greatest effect.

08:08.208 --> 08:11.959
We're looking at areas on
